  "displayTitle": "<span class=\"mw-page-title-main\">Honey Ham</span>",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output\">\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n\n<p><b>Honey Ham</b> is a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Meats\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Meats\">Meat</a> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Food\" title=\"Food\">Food</a> item produced in <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\">Crock Pot</a> by combining more than 1.5 units of Meats and 1 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Honey\" title=\"Honey\">Honey</a>. It takes 40 seconds to cook. Honey Ham is a well-rounded food providing 30 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Health\" title=\"Health\"><img alt=\"Health Icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Health_Icon.png/20px-Health_Icon.png?1ec0e6\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></a> (as much as a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Honey_Poultice\" title=\"Honey Poultice\">Honey Poultice</a>) and 75 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Hunger\" title=\"Hunger\"><img alt=\"Hunger Icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Hunger_Icon.png/20px-Hunger_Icon.png?9d0486\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></a>.\n</p><p>Adding more than 1 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Monster_Meat\" title=\"Monster Meat\">Monster Meat</a> will result in <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Monster_Lasagna\" title=\"Monster Lasagna\">Monster Lasagna</a>. Adding 1 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Twigs\" title=\"Twigs\">Twig</a> will result in <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Kabobs\" title=\"Kabobs\">Kabobs</a>. Adding <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Tallbird_Egg\" title=\"Tallbird Egg\">Tallbird Egg</a> will result in <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Bacon_and_Eggs\" title=\"Bacon and Eggs\">Bacon and Eggs</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Downloadable_Content\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Gift_Icon\" title=\"Gift Icon\"><img alt=\"Gift Icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Gift_Icon.png/32px-Gift_Icon.png?8b4efa\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Downloadable Content</span></h2>\n<p>In all <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/DLC\" class=\"mw-disambig\" title=\"DLC\">DLCs</a>, Honey Ham raises the player&#x27;s perceived temperature by 1 degree per second for 10 seconds when consumed. \n</p><p>In the <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve:_Shipwrecked\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve: Shipwrecked\">Shipwrecked</a></i> DLC as well as <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve_Together\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together\">Don&#x27;t Starve Together</a></i>, using Meats (such as <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Raw_Fish\" title=\"Raw Fish\">Raw Fish</a>) with more than 2.0 total <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot#Food_values\" title=\"Crock Pot\">fish value</a> will produce <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Seafood_Gumbo\" title=\"Seafood Gumbo\">Seafood Gumbo</a> instead.\n</p><p>In the <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve:_Hamlet\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve: Hamlet\">Hamlet</a></i> DLC, Honey Ham can be bought for 20 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Oinc\" title=\"Oinc\">Oincs</a> at <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Pig_Shops\" title=\"Pig Shops\">The Sterling Trough Deli</a>. It can also be used as a recipe for the player to create their own The Sterling Trough Deli structure via the <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Key_to_the_City\" title=\"Key to the City\">Key to the City</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Prerequisites\">Prerequisites</span></h2>\n<ul><li>Requires: <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Meats\" title=\"Meats\"><img alt=\"Meats Crock Pot(NoMoleworm).png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Meats_Crock_Pot%28NoMoleworm%29.png?959309\" width=\"565\" height=\"108\"></a></li>\n<li>Requires: <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Honey\" title=\"Honey\"><img alt=\"Honey.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Honey.png?d057e9\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></li>\n<li>Excludes: <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Twigs\" title=\"Twigs\"><img alt=\"Twigs.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Twigs.png?2fb15c\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Moleworm\" title=\"Moleworm\"><img alt=\"Moleworm.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Moleworm.png?2334f1\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Mandrake\" title=\"Mandrake\"><img alt=\"Mandrake.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Mandrake.png?c94a2f\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Tallbird_Egg\" title=\"Tallbird Egg\"><img alt=\"Tallbird Eggs.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Tallbird_Eggs.png?76d66a\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recipe\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Icon_Science\" title=\"Icon Science\"><img alt=\"Icon Science.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Icon_Science.png/32px-Icon_Science.png?63b6ec\" width=\"32\" height=\"39\"></a> Recipe</span></h2>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Meats\" title=\"Meats\"><img alt=\"Meats.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Meats.png?6eb40d\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>&gt;<b>1.5</b></p></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Honey\" title=\"Honey\"><img alt=\"Honey.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Honey.png?d057e9\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Filler\" title=\"Filler\"><img alt=\"Filler.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Filler.png?b5d099\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Honey_Ham\" title=\"Honey Ham\"><img alt=\"Honey Ham.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Honey_Ham.png?d02fb1\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Examples\">Examples</span></h2>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Morsel\" title=\"Morsel\"><img alt=\"Morsel.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Morsel.png?fe6bb2\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>2</b></p></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Monster_Meat\" title=\"Monster Meat\"><img alt=\"Monster Meat.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Monster_Meat.png?9251b3\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Honey\" title=\"Honey\"><img alt=\"Honey.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Honey.png?d057e9\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Honey_Ham\" title=\"Honey Ham\"><img alt=\"Honey Ham.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Honey_Ham.png?d02fb1\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Meat\" title=\"Meat\"><img alt=\"Meat.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Meat.png?ff3bf2\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Monster_Meat\" title=\"Monster Meat\"><img alt=\"Monster Meat.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Monster_Meat.png?9251b3\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Honey\" title=\"Honey\"><img alt=\"Honey.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Honey.png?d057e9\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Berry\" title=\"Berry\"><img alt=\"Berry.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Berry.png?ddd757\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Honey_Ham\" title=\"Honey Ham\"><img alt=\"Honey Ham.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Honey_Ham.png?d02fb1\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table><table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Normal_Meats\" title=\"Normal Meats\"><img alt=\"Normal Meats.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Normal_Meats.png?9e28e2\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>2</b></p></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Honey\" title=\"Honey\"><img alt=\"Honey.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Honey.png?d057e9\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>2</b></p></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Honey_Ham\" title=\"Honey Ham\"><img alt=\"Honey Ham.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Honey_Ham.png?d02fb1\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Normal_Meats\" title=\"Normal Meats\"><img alt=\"Normal Meats.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Normal_Meats.png?9e28e2\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Monster_Meats\" title=\"Monster Meats\"><img alt=\"Monster Meats.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Monster_Meats.png?c5a3b6\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Honey\" title=\"Honey\"><img alt=\"Honey.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Honey.png?d057e9\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Ice\" title=\"Ice\"><img alt=\"Ice.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Ice.png?8c6842\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Honey_Ham\" title=\"Honey Ham\"><img alt=\"Honey Ham.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Honey_Ham.png?d02fb1\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Reign_of_Giants\" title=\"Reign of Giants\"><img alt=\"Reign of Giants icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Reign_of_Giants_icon.png/64px-Reign_of_Giants_icon.png?12c8d5\" width=\"64\" height=\"70\"></a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Monster_Meats\" title=\"Monster Meats\"><img alt=\"Monster Meats.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Monster_Meats.png?c5a3b6\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Raw_Fishes\" title=\"Raw Fishes\"><img alt=\"Raw Fishes.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Raw_Fishes.png?7edcb9\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Small_Jerky\" title=\"Small Jerky\"><img alt=\"Small Jerky.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Small_Jerky.png?23f97d\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Honey\" title=\"Honey\"><img alt=\"Honey.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Honey.png?d057e9\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Honey_Ham\" title=\"Honey Ham\"><img alt=\"Honey Ham.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Honey_Ham.png?d02fb1\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Shipwrecked\" title=\"Shipwrecked\"><img alt=\"Shipwrecked icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Shipwrecked_icon.png/64px-Shipwrecked_icon.png?3f6ffb\" width=\"64\" height=\"70\"></a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Usage\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Icon_Tools\" title=\"Icon Tools\"><img alt=\"Icon Tools.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Icon_Tools.png/32px-Icon_Tools.png?f672d4\" width=\"32\" height=\"39\"></a> Usage</span></h2>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Honey_Ham\" title=\"Honey Ham\"><img alt=\"Honey Ham.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Honey_Ham.png?d02fb1\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Pig_Skin\" title=\"Pig Skin\"><img alt=\"Pig Skin.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Pig_Skin.png?3a7624\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>4</b></p></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Boards\" title=\"Boards\"><img alt=\"Boards.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Boards.png?79a528\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>4</b></p></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Key_to_the_City\" title=\"Key to the City\"><img alt=\"Key to the City.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Key_to_the_City.png/42px-Key_to_the_City.png?775850\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/The_Sterling_Trough_Deli\" title=\"The Sterling Trough Deli\"><img alt=\"The Sterling Trough Deli.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/The_Sterling_Trough_Deli.png?175ba8\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Hamlet\" title=\"Hamlet\"><img alt=\"Hamlet icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Hamlet_icon.png/64px-Hamlet_icon.png?e04a83\" width=\"64\" height=\"70\"></a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Trivia\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Placeholder\" title=\"Placeholder\"><img alt=\"Placeholder.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Placeholder.png/32px-Placeholder.png?210282\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Trivia</span></h2>\n<ul><li>During the <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Pig_Fiesta\" title=\"Pig Fiesta\">Pig Fiesta</a> event in <i>Hamlet</i>, Honey Ham takes on a more festive appearance.</li></ul>\n<div></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Gallery\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Blueprint\" title=\"Blueprint\"><img alt=\"Blueprint.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Blueprint.png/32px-Blueprint.png?80b6b5\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Gallery</span></h2>\n<ul class=\"gallery mw-gallery-traditional\">\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:The_Starver%27s_Carol.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Honey Ham in the Winter&#x27;s Feast update poster.\"><img alt=\"Honey Ham in the Winter&#x27;s Feast update poster.\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/The_Starver%27s_Carol.png/120px-The_Starver%27s_Carol.png?4b6f0e\" width=\"120\" height=\"119\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">Honey Ham in the <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Winter%27s_Feast\" title=\"Winter&#x27;s Feast\">Winter&#x27;s Feast</a></i> update poster.</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:CD_honeyham.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Original HD icon from Bonus Materials from CD Don&#x27;t Starve.\"><img alt=\"Original HD icon from Bonus Materials from CD Don&#x27;t Starve.\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/CD_honeyham.png/120px-CD_honeyham.png?7306d1\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">Original HD icon from Bonus Materials from <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/CD_Don%27t_Starve\" title=\"CD Don&#x27;t Starve\">CD Don&#x27;t Starve</a>.</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"tabber tabber--init\"><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"By_Type-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Honey_Ham#By_Type-0\">By Type</a><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"By_Crock_Pot_Value-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Honey_Ham#By_Crock_Pot_Value-0\">By Crock Pot Value</a><section class=\"tabber__section\"><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></section></div>\n\n\n\n\n</div>",
