  "plainText": "Don't Starve\nTogether\nHoney Ham\nNormal\nPig Fiesta\nFood Info\n75\n30\n5\nMeat\nObject Info\n15 Days\nCan be Burned\n40\nSource\n: ( ×20)\nCooking Info\n>1.5 x1 x1\n40 sec\n2\nMiscellaneous\n\"honeyham\"\n“Sweet and savory.”\n–Wilson\n“Fire, ham and honey go well together.”\n–Willow\n“Big meat with sweet is good meat.”\n–Wolfgang\n“A sweet sauce for this creature's sweet embrace.”\n–Wendy\n“HIGH QUALITY BIOFUEL DETECTED”\n–WX-78\n“Honey was the only sweetener I used for this lovely ham.”\n–Wickerbottom\n“But it's not a holiday...”\n–Woodie\n“Tender.”\n–Maxwell\n“A veritable feast of meat and sweetener.”\n–Wagstaff\n“A hearty feast!”\n–Wigfrid\n“Ooo, tasty!”\n–Webber\n“Is it a special occasion?”\n–Walani\n“Comfort food!”\n–Warly\n“A feast fit fer piratin'!”\n–Woodlegs\n“'TIS POUND O' FLESH”\n–Wilba\n“Poor Twirly Tail...”\n–Wormwood\n“Sticks to your ribs. And to your hands.”\n–Wheeler\n“Think I could fit that whole thing in my mouth?”\n–Winona\n“Mortals have so many ways of preparing meat.”\n–Wortox\n“Ruined honey with Pigmeat!!”\n–Wurt\n“Sweet pig meat!”\n–Walter\n“You can't go wrong dousing something in honey.”\n–Wanda\nHoney Ham is a Meat Food item produced in Crock Pot by combining more than 1.5 units of Meats and 1 Honey. It takes 40 seconds to cook. Honey Ham is a well-rounded food providing 30 (as much as a Honey Poultice) and 75 .\nAdding more than 1 Monster Meat will result in Monster Lasagna. Adding 1 Twig will result in Kabobs. Adding Tallbird Egg will result in Bacon and Eggs.\nDownloadable Content[edit | edit source]\nIn all DLCs, Honey Ham raises the player's perceived temperature by 1 degree per second for 10 seconds when consumed.\nIn the Shipwrecked DLC as well as Don't Starve Together, using Meats (such as Raw Fish) with more than 2.0 total fish value will produce Seafood Gumbo instead.\nIn the Hamlet DLC, Honey Ham can be bought for 20 Oincs at The Sterling Trough Deli. It can also be used as a recipe for the player to create their own The Sterling Trough Deli structure via the Key to the City.\nPrerequisites[edit | edit source]\nRequires:\nRequires:\nExcludes:\nRecipe[edit | edit source]\n>1.5\nExamples[edit | edit source]\n×2\n×2\n×2\nUsage[edit | edit source]\n×4\n×4\nTrivia[edit | edit source]\nDuring the Pig Fiesta event in Hamlet, Honey Ham takes on a more festive appearance.\nGallery[edit | edit source]\nHoney Ham in the Winter's Feast update poster.\nOriginal HD icon from Bonus Materials from CD Don't Starve.\nBy TypeBy Crock Pot Value\nView or edit this template\nFood and Edible Items (by Food Type)\nVeggie\nSeeds\nMeat\nGoodies\nGeneric\nHorrible\nRoughage\nElementals\nBurnt\nRaw\nGears\nGold Dust\nBerry\nWood\nNitre\nLunar Shards\nView or edit this template\nFood and Edible Items (by Food Value)\nMeats\nFishes\nVegetables\nFruits\nMonster Food\nEggs\nDairy\nSweetener\nFrozen\nInedibles\nMagic\nFat\nSeed\nJellyfish\nBone\nFilter\nAntihistamine\nDecoration\nBug\nNo Value Food",
