  "wikitext": "{{Navbutton/Separation}}\n{{Object Infobox\n|foodType = [[Food_Type#Meat|Meat]] [[File:Meats.png|32px|link=Food_Type#Meat]]\n|foodRecipe = {{Pic|32px|Meats}}>1.5 {{Pic|32px|Honey}}x1 {{Pic|32px|Filler}}x1\n|canBeBurned=1\n|icon = <gallery>\nHoney Ham.png|Normal\nHoney Ham (Pig Fiesta).png|Pig Fiesta\n</gallery>\n|image = Honey Ham Dropped.png\n|spoil          = 15 Days\n|stack          = 40\n|hpRestored     = 30\n|hungerRestored = 75\n|sanityRestored = 5\n|cooktime       = 40 sec\n|priority       = 2\n|soldBy         ={{Ham}}: {{Pic|32|The Sterling Trough Deli}} ({{Pic|24|Oinc}} &times;20)\n|spawnCode      = \"honeyham\"\n}}\n{{Quotes\n|wilson = Sweet and savory.\n|willow = Fire, ham and honey go well together.\n|wolfgang = Big meat with sweet is good meat.\n|wendy = A sweet sauce for this creature's sweet embrace.\n|wx78 = HIGH QUALITY BIOFUEL DETECTED\n|wickerbottom = Honey was the only sweetener I used for this lovely ham.\n|woodie = But it's not a holiday...\n|maxwell = Tender.\n|wagstaff = A veritable feast of meat and sweetener.\n|wigfrid = A hearty feast!\n|webber = Ooo, tasty!\n|walani = Is it a special occasion?\n|warly = Comfort food!\n|woodlegs = A feast fit fer piratin'!\n|wilba = 'TIS POUND O' FLESH\n|wormwood = Poor Twirly Tail...\n|wheeler = Sticks to your ribs. And to your hands.\n|winona = Think I could fit that whole thing in my mouth?\n|wortox = Mortals have so many ways of preparing meat.\n|wurt = Ruined honey with Pigmeat!!\n|walter = Sweet pig meat!\n|wanda = You can't go wrong dousing something in honey.\n|choose = walter\n}}\n'''Honey Ham''' is a [[Meats|Meat]] [[Food]] item produced in [[Crock Pot]] by combining more than 1.5 units of Meats and 1 [[Honey]]. It takes 40 seconds to cook. Honey Ham is a well-rounded food providing 30 {{Hp}} (as much as a [[Honey Poultice]]) and 75 {{Hunger}}.\n\nAdding more than 1 [[Monster Meat]] will result in [[Monster Lasagna]]. Adding 1 [[Twigs|Twig]] will result in [[Kabobs]]. Adding [[Tallbird Egg]] will result in [[Bacon and Eggs]].\n__NOTOC__\n== {{Pic32|Gift Icon}} Downloadable Content ==\nIn all [[DLC]]s, Honey Ham raises the player's perceived temperature by 1 degree per second for 10 seconds when consumed. \n\nIn the ''[[Don't Starve: Shipwrecked|Shipwrecked]]'' DLC as well as ''[[Don't Starve Together]]'', using Meats (such as [[Raw Fish]]) with more than 2.0 total [[Crock Pot#Food values|fish value]] will produce [[Seafood Gumbo]] instead.\n\nIn the ''[[Don't Starve: Hamlet|Hamlet]]'' DLC, Honey Ham can be bought for 20 [[Oinc]]s at [[Pig Shops|The Sterling Trough Deli]]. It can also be used as a recipe for the player to create their own The Sterling Trough Deli structure via the [[Key to the City]].\n\n== Prerequisites ==\n* Requires: [[File:Meats Crock Pot(NoMoleworm).png|link=Meats]]\n* Requires: [[File:Honey.png|link=Honey]]\n* Excludes: [[File:Twigs.png|link=Twigs]][[File:Moleworm.png|link=Moleworm]][[File:Mandrake.png|link=Mandrake]][[File:Tallbird Eggs.png|link=Tallbird Egg]]\n\n== {{pic|32|Icon Science}} Recipe ==\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Meats\n|count1 = 1.5\n|item2 = Honey\n|item3 = Filler\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Honey Ham\n|comparator1=>}}\n\n== Examples ==\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Morsel\n|count1 = 2\n|item2 = Monster Meat\n|item3 = Honey\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Honey Ham\n}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Meat\n|item2 = Monster Meat\n|item3 = Honey\n|item4 = Berry\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Honey Ham\n}}{{Recipe\n|item1 = Normal Meats\n|item3 = Honey\n|count3 = 2\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Honey Ham\n|count1=2}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Normal Meats\n|item2 = Monster Meats\n|item3 = Honey\n|item4 = Ice\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Honey Ham\n|dlc = Reign of Giants\n}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Monster Meats\n|item2 = Raw Fishes\n|item3 = Small Jerky\n|item4 = Honey\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Honey Ham\n|dlc = Shipwrecked\n}}\n\n=={{pic32|Icon Tools}} Usage ==\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Honey Ham\n|item2 = Pig Skin\n|count2 = 4\n|item3 = Boards\n|count3 = 4\n|result = The Sterling Trough Deli\n|tool = Key to the City\n|dlc = Hamlet\n}}\n\n== {{Pic32|Placeholder}} Trivia ==\n* During the [[Pig Fiesta]] event in ''Hamlet'', Honey Ham takes on a more festive appearance.\n{{clear}}\n\n== {{pic32|Blueprint}} Gallery ==\n<gallery captionalign=\"center\" hideaddbutton=\"true\">\nThe Starver's Carol.png|Honey Ham in the ''[[Winter's Feast]]'' update poster.\nCD honeyham.png|Original HD icon from Bonus Materials from [[CD Don't Starve]].\n</gallery>\n{{Crock Pot Food}}\n__NOTOC__\n[[Category:Crock Pot Recipes]]\n[[Category:Food]]\n[[Category:Flammable Objects]]\n[[Category:Healing]]\n[[Category:Meats]]\n[[Category:Sanity Boost]]\n[[Category:Perishables]]\n[[Category:Warmth]]\n[[ru:Медовый рулет]]\n[[fr:jambon au miel]]\n[[vi:Giăm Bông Mật Ong]]\n[[zh:蜂蜜火腿]]"
